      public double monthlyInterest()
      Calculates and returns the monthly interest of the account. Rate depends on whether the account balance is greater or equal to MIN_BALANCE_FOR_LOYAL). If loyal, the LOYAL_INTEREST_RATE is used;
      Overrides:
      monthlyInterest in class Savings
      Returns:

    • monthlyFee

      public double monthlyFee()
      Calculates and return the monthly fee
      Overrides:
      monthlyFee in class Savings
      Returns:
      10 if balance is greater and equal to 2000 and withdrawal greater than 3, 35 if it is just withdrawal is greater than 3, 25 if balance less than 2000 and withdrawal less than equal to 3. Otherwise 0 if balance is greater and equal to MIN_BALANCE_FOR_LOYAL, false otherwise
